dc_title_s.dc_title_s: McGregor 000003016 - 1649 - Nova Anglia Novvm Belgium et Virginia

dc_description_s.dc_description_s:
* Variant Tile: Nova Anglia, Novum Belgium et Virginia
* Author: Jansson, Jan
* Credit: Area Table 755 1636 Jansson 1649
* Published: Amstelodami : Johannes Janssonius Excudit, [ca.1649]
        * Relief shown pictorially.
        * Scale in strapwork box right lower recto.
        * On verso: German text, captioned "New Belgica und New Anglia" and "New Anglia"; signature mark Ccc; catchword New.
        * Burden, State 1, from 1649 edition of Newer Atlas (Mercator/Hondius atlas variant).
        * Derived from 1630 map of Johannes de Laet.
